message: Same editor continues to make this an entry about Jesse Rothstein and to eliminate other information about Hoxby's research
Once again this editor wishes to give disproportionate coverage to Rothstein, who can be covered on entries devoted to him

Undid revision 655652740.  This is not an entry devoted to Jesse Rothstein; an editor repeatedly eliminates information regarding Hoxby's research and activities and introduces disproportionate coverage of Rothstein.
Reintroduced links to media coverage of public interest
Undid malicious removal of informative content
